The <strong><code>flex-basis</code></strong> <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</a> property sets the initial main size of a flex item. It sets the size of the content box unless otherwise set with <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/box-sizing" title="The box-sizing CSS property sets how the total width and height of an element is calculated."><code>box-sizing</code></a>.